| Opaque reactivity in getAutosaveLabel | review/+page.svelte | 129, 1238 | Low-Medium | Clarity |
| Incomplete synthetic Change object | review/+page.svelte | 1150-1160 | Medium | Type contract |
| No constants for lint categories | Multiple | Multiple | Low | DRY |
| State inconsistency check | review/+page.svelte | 596-600 | Low | Acceptable pattern |
| Stale change fallback | review/+page.svelte | 1148-1161 | Low | Graceful degradation |

